=The Sun in the Dark=

26
00:01:36,672 --> 00:01:38,912
=Episode 22=

27
00:01:53,659 --> 00:01:54,340
You may leave.

28
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:55,620
Yes.

29
00:02:02,939 --> 00:02:04,140
If you take these off again,

30
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:06,060
I'll slaughter all until no soul

31
00:02:06,459 --> 00:02:07,939
remains across the Three Realms.

32
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:16,939
You look great.

33
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,900
Wear these for our wedding ceremony.

34
00:02:20,819 --> 00:02:22,419
I never knew you looked so great in red.

35
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:26,340
We'll need more red garments
in your wardrobe.

36
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:29,939
What's with that look?

37
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,300
Our wedding approaches swiftly.

38
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:34,219
You should smile more.

39
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,460
My Lord,

40
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:41,460
the wedding arrangements are complete.

41
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:44,699
I see.

42
00:02:46,699 --> 00:02:47,180
Let's go.

43
00:03:07,776 --> 00:03:11,600
♪The moon climbs branches
as night winds whisper♪

44
00:03:11,648 --> 00:03:15,488
♪Singing with wine
under chaotic starlight♪

45
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:19,440
♪Only one lamp burning
in the endless nights♪

46
00:03:22,099 --> 00:03:23,340
(You once promised)

47
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:26,659
to show me every earthly joy.

48
00:03:28,659 --> 00:03:30,460
If I may make one final wish,

49
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:33,580
it's to become your bride.

50
00:03:34,659 --> 00:03:35,300
Okay.

51
00:03:38,139 --> 00:03:39,379
