52
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:47,840
♪I remember you silently
through calm and storm♪

53
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:54,016
♪A single promise settled in my heart,
cherished ever since♪

54
00:03:56,720 --> 00:04:03,560
♪Some would distill time into tales♪

55
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:05,939
(Ye Chenyuan,)

56
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:08,780
(now)

57
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:12,620
(we'll finally unite
as true husband and wife.)

58
00:04:18,752 --> 00:04:26,208
(Yunxiu Pavilion)

59
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:36,100
Those who obstruct me today

60
00:04:36,779 --> 00:04:37,740
die.

61
00:04:38,579 --> 00:04:39,459
When striking,

62
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:40,500
steady your hands.

63
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:42,660
Keep your stance rooted.

64
00:04:52,899 --> 00:04:53,740
What brings you here?

65
00:04:53,899 --> 00:04:54,500
Halt.

66
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:00,939
Yunya,

67
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:02,300
why are you here?

68
00:05:03,339 --> 00:05:05,339
Relax. I came alone.

69
00:05:06,459 --> 00:05:09,500
Bai Xiaoying and I
follow divergent paths now.

70
00:05:10,259 --> 00:05:11,060
From now on,

71
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,300
I'll no longer serve her interests.

72
00:05:15,819 --> 00:05:16,620
Yunya,

73
00:05:17,259 --> 00:05:19,779
you aided Bai Xiaoying's assault
on the immortal sects

74
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:22,060
and then helped her
slaughter our members.

75
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:24,860
Now you come crawling like a stray dog,

76
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,139
seeking our sanctuary?

77
00:05:26,459 --> 00:05:27,920
Why should we trust you?

78
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:39,459
My intimate knowledge
of their operations

79
00:05:39,899 --> 00:05:41,660
and this blade at your throat.

80
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:42,459
You!

81
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:44,560
Yunya,

82
00:05:45,139 --> 00:05:45,899
stop.

83
00:05:47,019 --> 00:05:47,819
Elder Kongming,

84
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:49,899
I vouch for him.

85
00:05:50,939 --> 00:05:52,139
Given our current strength,

86
00:05:52,379 --> 00:05:53,779
he gains nothing through deception.

87
00:05:54,379 --> 00:05:55,060
Moreover,

88
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,540
we need him more than he needs us.

89
00:06:12,339 --> 00:06:13,620
They endured Bai Xiaoying's

90
00:06:13,899 --> 00:06:15,660
unspeakable torments.

91
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:17,939
Their wariness is understandable.

92
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:21,259
Pay it no mind.

93
00:06:22,339 --> 00:06:23,420
Let's discuss this outside.

94
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:28,939
During our immortal sect days,

95
00:06:29,379 --> 00:06:30,860
you smuggled medicine to me.

96
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,600
That's how I knew

97
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,180
your honor still burned bright

98
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,939
and loyalty persisted.

99
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:46,060
Immortal Xiyuan
is gathering forces covertly.

100
00:06:47,019 --> 00:06:48,379
During Bai Xiaoying's wedding,

101
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,620
we'll storm the Nine Heavens

102
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:52,819
and save my father.

103
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:55,720
Attacking during the wedding is wise.

104
00:06:57,579 --> 00:06:58,540
But my true aim

105
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,180
isn't the Immortal Lord

106
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:02,779
but Bai Xiaoying herself.

107
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,300
Do you plan to kill her?

108
00:07:13,379 --> 00:07:14,579
I'd never do that.

109
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,579
I mean to claim her

110
00:07:18,259 --> 00:07:20,060
and make her mine alone.

111
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:24,300
You know my feelings for you.

112
00:07:25,899 --> 00:07:27,939
Why torture me with these words?

113
00:07:29,019 --> 00:07:29,740
Yes.

114
00:07:30,819 --> 00:07:32,939
I've long known
your infatuation with her.

115
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:35,819
That's why I hate her so much.

116
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:39,019
But you've broken from her faction.

117
00:07:39,860 --> 00:07:41,779
Why cling to this obsession?

118
00:07:43,939 --> 00:07:44,860
Obsession?

119
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:48,500
Irony drips

120
00:07:48,579 --> 00:07:51,459
hearing this from you of all people,
who kept pestering me earlier.

121
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:53,180
Yes.

122
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,779
When desperate efforts

123
00:07:55,819 --> 00:07:57,899
can't match a rival in love's
casual gesture,

124
00:07:58,899 --> 00:08:00,100
madness becomes sanctuary.

125
00:08:00,579 --> 00:08:02,819
So you're joining us
just to use our forces

126
00:08:02,819 --> 00:08:04,139
for your conquest of her?

127
00:08:11,139 --> 00:08:12,860
Aren't you afraid I'll expel you?

128
00:08:14,019 --> 00:08:16,040
That would doom your scheme.

129
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:19,339
Do as you will.

130
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:21,819
But only through me

131
00:08:22,459 --> 00:08:24,100
can your father be saved.

132
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,519
The choice is yours.

133
00:08:51,139 --> 00:08:51,779
What's wrong?

134
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:54,460
What?

135
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,820
You rarely show concern for me.

136
00:08:57,100 --> 00:08:58,580
Yet you overreact to a single cough?

137
00:08:59,179 --> 00:08:59,379
I...

138
00:08:59,419 --> 00:09:00,659
Do you want me unwell?

139
00:09:01,299 --> 00:09:02,659
So no one will force you to marry?

140
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:08,659
Just to be clear, I'm fine.

141
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,179
Your wish won't come true.

142
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,340
You're irritating me now.

143
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,220
Get out.

144
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:28,860
(In his heart,)

145
00:09:29,659 --> 00:09:31,899
(I'm just an irredeemable demon.)

146
00:09:33,059 --> 00:09:34,460
(Why would he ever care about me?)

147
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,700
(I should be used to this.)

148
00:09:54,539 --> 00:09:55,620
I made this soup.

149
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:57,620
Drink it while it's warm.

150
00:10:00,659 --> 00:10:01,899
I never asked you to do this.

151
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:05,980
I did it because I wanted to.

152
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:10,779
I was just scolding you.

153
00:10:11,899 --> 00:10:12,820
Aren't you angry?

154
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,940
Certain images keep appearing in my mind

155
00:10:17,659 --> 00:10:18,620
with you in them.

156
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:24,139
But I don't understand why

157
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,340
I keep thinking of you.

158
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:32,980
(He's regaining
some spiritual awareness?)

159
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,259
Then feed me.

160
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:42,299
And I'll tell you.

161
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:00,980
(I can't reveal
the full truth to him yet.)

162
00:11:06,259 --> 00:11:07,100
Actually,

163
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:10,379
we met long ago.

164
00:11:11,899 --> 00:11:13,259
To put it simply,

165
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:17,659
we were lovers in past lives.

166
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,779
I knew you felt familiar.

167
00:11:22,740 --> 00:11:24,259
What happened between us then?

168
00:11:28,139 --> 00:11:29,139
I don't remember clearly.

169
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,059
But none of that matters.

170
00:11:35,019 --> 00:11:36,259
What's important between us

171
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,379
isn't our past

172
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:40,100
or our future,

173
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:42,340
but the present.

174
00:11:44,899 --> 00:11:46,940
If we cherish every current moment,

175
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:48,500
that's enough.

176
00:12:10,019 --> 00:12:10,779
In three days,

177
00:12:11,059 --> 00:12:12,700
it's Bai Xiaoying's wedding ceremony.

178
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:16,019
We'll seize this chance
to storm back to the Nine Heavens

179
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:17,220
and save our lord.

180
00:12:18,059 --> 00:12:19,139
Are you prepared?

181
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:20,299
- We are!
- We are!

182
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:38,179
What's wrong?

183
00:12:40,299 --> 00:12:41,019
I'm fine.

184
00:12:42,419 --> 00:12:43,980
It's been a long day

185
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:46,740
and I'm truly tired today.

186
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:49,259
Why not carry me to the hot spring?

187
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:50,379
We're not going today.

188
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:53,019
I've realized

189
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:56,019
you're not actually torturing me.

190
00:12:56,899 --> 00:12:58,220
You're helping me recover.

191
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:00,740
If this harms you,

192
00:13:02,019 --> 00:13:02,940
I don't want it.

193
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:07,899
But I'm willing.

194
00:13:08,299 --> 00:13:10,500
Your full recovery is my greatest wish.

195
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:13,259
Besides, I know my own condition.

196
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:15,500
Take me there.

197
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:15,980
No.

198
00:13:50,779 --> 00:13:51,659
In strategy,

199
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:54,220
you still have much to learn.

200
00:13:55,379 --> 00:13:56,700
You must stop this.

201
00:13:59,659 --> 00:14:00,580
For your sake,

202
00:14:02,059 --> 00:14:03,460
I'll do anything.

203
00:14:06,659 --> 00:14:08,740
Two days' rest will restore me.

204
00:14:09,419 --> 00:14:10,419
Don't worry.

205
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,379
How could I not worry?

206
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,340
Today's the lantern festival.

207
00:14:23,059 --> 00:14:24,832
Let's release lanterns
in the Mortal Realm.

208
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,100
- It's the Night Deity.
- Let's go.

209
00:14:42,059 --> 00:14:43,460
Seems on this Qixi Festival,

210
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:45,500
we're the only ones floating lanterns.

211
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:49,700
Come.

212
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:03,980
I'll teach you.

213
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,980
First, close your eyes

214
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:19,340
and make a wish.

215
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:46,379
This feels so familiar.

216
00:15:51,899 --> 00:15:53,860
There was someone beside me then.

217
00:15:58,940 --> 00:15:59,700
It was you.

218
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:11,139
Whether in the past

219
00:16:12,379 --> 00:16:13,379
or present times,

220
00:16:14,820 --> 00:16:16,019
the person by your side

221
00:16:16,379 --> 00:16:17,179
has always been me.

222
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,539
Though my memories remain unclear,

223
00:16:30,179 --> 00:16:30,860
whenever

224
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:32,899
I'm with you,

225
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:37,700
certain images surface in my mind.

226
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:39,460
It makes me

227
00:16:40,779 --> 00:16:42,779
believe you must be
someone important to me.

228
00:16:45,659 --> 00:16:46,740
I hope someday

229
00:16:48,299 --> 00:16:48,980
you can

230
00:16:49,539 --> 00:16:51,620
tell me everything completely.

231
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,899
That day will come.

232
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:58,779
When it does,

233
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:01,980
I'll tell you everything.

234
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:13,700
What wish did you make just now?

235
00:17:15,779 --> 00:17:17,339
I hope you can let go of your hatred

236
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:20,380
and let the world have peace.

237
00:17:29,779 --> 00:17:30,980
What if I refuse?

238
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:34,299
If you could only choose one

239
00:17:36,019 --> 00:17:37,180
between world peace and me,

240
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,339
what would you choose?

241
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:42,940
I choose world peace.

242
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:49,619
Because I know

243
00:17:50,099 --> 00:17:51,539
that's the real you.

244
00:17:54,779 --> 00:17:55,500
Turn back now.

245
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,180
But there's no turning back for me.

246
00:18:10,259 --> 00:18:10,980
Listen.

247
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,819
Even if you give up on yourself,

248
00:18:14,779 --> 00:18:16,140
I'll never give up on you.

249
00:18:48,099 --> 00:18:50,539
It's time for their wedding ceremony.

250
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:52,579
Aren't you going to act?

251
00:19:14,019 --> 00:19:15,380
The auspicious hour has arrived.

252
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:17,380
Welcome the newlyweds!

253
00:19:30,048 --> 00:19:35,000
♪Flickering candles
cast our silhouettes♪

254
00:19:40,980 --> 00:19:42,700
First bow to heaven and earth.

255
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:48,180
Second bow to the parents.

256
00:19:49,408 --> 00:19:54,529
♪I watch splendor fade,
leaving solitude♪

257
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:56,779
Final bow to each other.

258
00:19:59,104 --> 00:20:02,528
♪But shattered mirrors never mend♪

259
00:20:02,528 --> 00:20:08,460
♪I don't know
whether to forget or remember♪

260
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,380
The ceremony concluded.

261
00:20:10,259 --> 00:20:11,539
To the bridal chamber.

262
00:20:12,539 --> 00:20:13,099
Wait.

263
00:20:14,859 --> 00:20:16,299
Going to the chamber now

264
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:17,460
would be too dull.

265
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:21,299
Since this is my wedding day,

266
00:20:22,019 --> 00:20:23,180
we'll follow my rules.

267
00:20:24,019 --> 00:20:24,700
Honey,

268
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,180
isn't that right?

269
00:20:28,019 --> 00:20:28,420
Yes.

270
00:20:29,339 --> 00:20:30,140
I'll listen to you.

271
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:38,496
♪Even crescent moons find fullness♪

272
00:20:38,555 --> 00:20:41,740
♪But shattered mirrors never mend♪

273
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:42,819
I want to drink

274
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:44,220
the nuptial wine with you

275
00:20:45,019 --> 00:20:46,420
with everyone here as witnesses.

276
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:51,872
♪Borrowing a full moon from heaven♪

277
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:55,520
♪Cradling moonlight like broken glass♪

278
00:20:55,744 --> 00:21:03,424
♪Cloaked in moonlight,
I journey without return♪

279
00:21:19,380 --> 00:21:20,420
Let's go to the chamber.

280
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:38,779
Xiaoying,

281
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:43,180
what have you done to me?

282
00:21:44,859 --> 00:21:45,539
