- Step back!

299
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,339
Hua Yuying,

300
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:39,539
I entrust Ye Chenyuan to you.

301
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:42,059
Xiaoying!

302
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,680
