304
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:53,568
♪Storms disperse.
Drunken reunions trace past bonds♪

305
00:22:54,259 --> 00:22:56,539
By transferring all my power to you,

306
00:22:57,500 --> 00:22:58,900
I can finally rest easy.

307
00:23:00,660 --> 00:23:02,299
This is the last gift I can give you.

308
00:23:02,848 --> 00:23:05,680
♪Cutting a fragment of time♪

309
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:09,320
♪Shattered stars can't compare
to my resolve with you♪

310
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:15,392
♪Though countless sorrows
may fall like petals♪

311
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:18,240
♪For this stretch of time♪

312
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:22,520
♪Walk with you through life and death♪

313
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:24,880
♪Carving your essence in my heart♪

314
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:29,152
♪Creating life's fairest memory♪

315
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:45,800
♪Searching through half a lifetime,
I rest with the breeze as my pillow♪

316
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:48,520
♪The bright moon's yearning
echoes through lonely strings♪

317
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,560
♪Gazing across the mortal realm♪

318
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:54,272
♪She appears where lanterns fade♪

319
00:23:55,456 --> 00:23:58,320
♪Storms disperse.
