safe and sound.

328
00:24:21,728 --> 00:24:23,600
♪Carving your essence in my heart♪

329
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:28,704
♪Creating life's fairest memory♪

330
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:36,180
