335
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,579
I'll take it myself.

336
00:25:11,220 --> 00:25:12,940
Bai Xiaoying, where is Immortal Lord?

337
00:25:13,019 --> 00:25:13,900
Release him at once

338
00:25:14,059 --> 00:25:15,180
