342
00:25:23,019 --> 00:25:25,539
Haven't you committed enough vile deeds?

343
00:25:26,059 --> 00:25:26,900
What did you say?

344
00:25:28,019 --> 00:25:28,980
Do you know

345
00:25:29,779 --> 00:25:32,700
the Night Deity should've perished
completely over a millennium ago?

346
00:25:33,099 --> 00:25:36,180
Your father
destroyed the Divine Sword's spirit,

347
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:39,140
causing the Night Deity
to revive every three centuries

348
00:25:39,579 --> 00:25:42,740
and plunging the Mortal Realm
into suffering for 1,500 years.

349
00:25:43,299 --> 00:25:45,740
All was just to make people worship him

350
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:48,180
and your Nine Heavens.

351
00:25:49,019 --> 00:25:51,779
Is this your so-called
'protecting the Three Realms'?

352
00:25:52,259 --> 00:25:52,819
Impossible!

353
00:25:53,019 --> 00:25:54,019
My father didn't do that.

354
00:25:54,539 --> 00:25:56,220
You're falsely slandering him.

355
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:57,740
I needn't slander him.

356
00:25:58,339 --> 00:25:59,740
Now that Yuan has revived,

357
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:00,660
Feng Changgeng

358
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,579
has no reason to remain in this world.

359
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:04,619
I'll kill him myself

360
00:26:04,779 --> 00:26:07,299
in mourning for all the dead
he had caused.

361
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:08,859
Bai Xiaoying!

362
00:26:08,859 --> 00:26:09,700
Form the array!

363
00:26:22,019 --> 00:26:22,579
Xiaoying?

364
00:26:24,099 --> 00:26:25,299
Kill the Night Deity now!

365
00:26:34,259 --> 00:26:35,380
Yunya, you!

366
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,380
If you kill her now,

367
00:26:37,779 --> 00:26:39,136
how do we save the Immortal Lord?

368
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,859
Your energy was drained.

369
00:26:44,339 --> 00:26:46,900
You must have used Night Deity's power
to revive Ye Chenyuan.

370
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:49,460
Then the Night Deity's power

371
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:50,980
must be within you now.

372
00:26:53,339 --> 00:26:53,819
Yuan,

373
00:26:54,339 --> 00:26:54,980
are you alright?

374
00:26:58,539 --> 00:26:59,420
His magic is weak.

375
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,019
He has no Night Deity's power.

376
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:08,900
(How is this possible?)

377
00:27:18,779 --> 00:27:20,339
Beings of the Three Realms,

378
00:27:20,819 --> 00:27:22,099
from this day forward,

379
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:24,059
I am

380
00:27:24,339 --> 00:27:25,500
the Night Deity!

381
00:27:41,180 --> 00:27:42,180
The Night Deity's power.

382
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:52,980
Father!

383
00:27:55,579 --> 00:27:56,339
Father,

384
00:27:56,779 --> 00:27:58,099
the energy surrounding you...

385
00:27:59,579 --> 00:28:00,500
is demonic energy?

386
00:28:20,339 --> 00:28:21,819
Without the Divine Sword

387
00:28:22,180 --> 00:28:23,859
to seal the Night Deity's power,

388
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:25,460
the Night Deity

389
00:28:25,900 --> 00:28:28,859
will never vanish.

390
00:28:30,019 --> 00:28:30,819
That's right.

391
00:28:31,299 --> 00:28:32,980
I am the Night Deity.

392
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,740
The Divine Sword is destroyed.

393
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:37,339
Nothing remains

394
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,180
that can threaten me now.

395
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:45,180
So Bai Xiaoying
was telling the truth all along.

396
00:28:48,380 --> 00:28:50,019
Judging by your look,

397
00:28:50,339 --> 00:28:52,420
you've only just figured it out,
haven't you?

398
00:28:52,819 --> 00:28:54,099
You planned this from the start!

399
00:28:55,299 --> 00:28:56,740
You used Yuan's revival

400
00:28:57,220 --> 00:28:59,299
to channel the Night Deity's power
through me.

401
00:28:59,779 --> 00:29:01,420
Yet I've kept my word.

402
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:04,059
Haven't I revived Ye Chenyuan?

403
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:05,700
Pity that

404
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:09,140
you're now useless and worthless trash

405
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:10,700
in my eyes.

406
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:12,819
Therefore,

407
00:29:13,220 --> 00:29:14,900
I must dispose of you.

408
00:29:16,299 --> 00:29:17,339
You'll not harm our Lord!

409
00:29:17,779 --> 00:29:18,619
Your Lord?

410
00:29:19,299 --> 00:29:20,619
I am the Night Deity.

411
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,579
I'm your true Lord.

412
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:24,500
From this moment onward,

413
00:29:25,220 --> 00:29:27,940
the Night Clan obeys only my commands.

414
00:29:29,180 --> 00:29:30,099
Kill them.

415
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:32,980
And I may still employ you.

416
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:36,339
That's right.

417
00:29:37,299 --> 00:29:37,940
The Night Clan

418
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,900
follows the strongest.

419
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:42,500
The weak either die

420
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:44,140
or submit.

421
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:49,099
But I despise hypocrites most
in this life.

422
00:29:50,180 --> 00:29:51,539
And you're one of them.

423
00:29:52,339 --> 00:29:55,019
I only acknowledge Ye Chenyuan
and Bai Xiaoying as my masters.

424
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:56,619
And you?

425
00:29:56,779 --> 00:29:57,700
Dream on!

426
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:01,500
Stubborn fool!

427
00:30:11,059 --> 00:30:11,940
You cur!

428
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:15,420
Kill me if you dare!

429
00:30:16,259 --> 00:30:17,299
