437
00:30:49,579 --> 00:30:50,859
in serving Lord Night Deity.

438
00:30:51,579 --> 00:30:52,539
Jiaotu,

439
00:30:52,619 --> 00:30:53,259
you!

440
00:30:55,180 --> 00:30:57,180
My loyalty lies with the Night Deity.

441
00:30:57,980 --> 00:30:59,019
Whoever holds that title

442
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:00,619
